---
import artistry1 from '../assets/artistry-1.jpg';
import artistry2 from '../assets/artistry-2.jpg';
---

<section id="past-projects" class="px-5 py-4">
  <main class="space-y-6">
    <h2
      class="text-3xl uppercase md:mb-10 sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl 2xl:8xl"
    >
      My past projects
    </h2>

    <section
      class="text-sm sm:flex sm:flex-row sm:justify-center sm:gap-10 sm:px-20 sm:flex-wrap md:flex-nowrap md:justify-between"
    >
      <figure class="space-y-4 sm:w-5/12 lg:w-auto">
        <figcaption class="text-center italic">
          Sunnyside agencly landing page (frontendmentor)
        </figcaption>
        <img src={artistry2.src} />
        <figcaption
          class="text-center sm:text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base xl:text-lg 2xl:text-xl"
        >
          Developed a user-friendly data compression system that provides
          efficient compression ratio and compression speed in regards with the
          time and speed of both compression and decompression.
        </figcaption>
      </figure>

      <figure class="space-y-4 sm:w-5/12 lg:w-auto">
        <figcaption class="text-center italic">Quote Generator</figcaption>
        <img src={artistry2.src} />
        <figcaption
          class="text-center sm:text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base xl:text-lg 2xl:text-xl"
        >
          Developed a user-friendly management system that can manage and secure
          trip and travel informaion efficiently.
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
      <figure class="space-y-4 sm:w-5/12 lg:w-auto">
        <figcaption class="text-center italic">Advice Generator App</figcaption>
        <img src={artistry1.src} />
        <figcaption
          class="text-center sm:text-xs md:text-sm lg:text-base xl:text-lg 2xl:text-xl"
        >
          Developed a responsive landing page that seamlessly adapts to various
          screen sizes and devices, ensuring an optimal user experience.
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </section>
  </main>
</section>
